collection.name: Chibi Apes
collection.description:
**3000 randomly generated 3D characters aping around the Ethereum blockchain. Every ape is created from 119 possible traits, where at least 4 traits differ, ensuring that each ape is highly unique!**  

All - [**Chibi Labs**](https://opensea.io/collection/chibi-labs)  
Gen 1 - [**Chibi Genesis**](https://opensea.io/collection/chibi-genesis)  
Gen 2 - [**Chibi Apes**](https://opensea.io/collection/chibi-apes)  
Gen 3 - [**Chibi Galaxy**](https://opensea.io/collection/chibi-galaxy)  
Frens - [**Chibi Frens**](https://opensea.io/collection/chibi-frens)
